{"tid":324352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗母子突然失蹤　警方發相尋人　","createTime":"2017-07-16T11:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T14:39:48.000Z","uid":20933,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"46797e9b1a4ce762f26330ea33b6e33e9008caa1","tid":324352,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:27:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170716/large/1500190890_1c46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170716%2Flarge%2F1500190890_1c46.jpg&h=45b84d93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一對母子於上周四(13/7)晚上約10時30分與家人電話聯絡後，便失去聯絡，其家人翌日到深水埗警署向警方報案。<br />\n<br />\n失蹤女子范云金(34歲)，身高約1.58米，肥身材，黃皮膚及蓄長黑髮；其子郭錦（10歲）身高約1.5米，瘦身材，黃皮膚及蓄短黑髮。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲，任何人士如有兩人消息或曾見過他們，請致3661 8813或3661 8804與調查人員或與任何一間警署聯絡。"},{"pid":"166c57ec0e0f3acb1581ed1a2903d689b53a50c8","tid":324352,"uid":4780,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:27:52.000Z","msg":"支那豬wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9344610d259c0fdb145b62e21afd0495db83b2b8","tid":324352,"uid":20227,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:32:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"440f71f07ef67594ad512640b7a4b3b7d151649c","tid":324352,"uid":54582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:37:47.000Z","msg":"No one cares"},{"pid":"214e863b2b01a1c06e15e752506ff91be2a9247f","tid":324352,"uid":11935,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:40:04.000Z","msg":"唔睇名,一睇相都知係蝗,已經唔洗睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n口德-50"},{"pid":"acc2ff548263a9cfb87adb2d34d688bf3c9ce3cd","tid":324352,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:41:57.000Z","msg":"死啦賤畜"},{"pid":"25538c0eb156b738adc24ef42f524fb16cf5b767","tid":324352,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,